<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Scope Rejected</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; } .container {
      max-width: 600px; margin: auto; padding: 24px; border: 1px solid #eee;
      border-radius: 8px; } .logo { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px; }
      .logo img { width: 120px; } .highlight { color:
      {{primaryColor}}; font-weight: bold; } .footer { font-size: 12px; color:
      #888; margin-top: 30px; text-align: center; }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="logo">
        <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="Scopology Logo" />
      </div>

      <p>Hi {{clientName}},</p>

      <p>
        We appreciate your effort in submitting a scope titled
        <strong>"{{scopeTitle}}"</strong>
        with the nature of work
        <strong>"{{natureOfWork}}"</strong>.
      </p>

      <p>
        However, after reviewing the submission, it has been
        <span class="highlight">rejected</span>.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>Reason for rejection:</strong><br />
        {{rejectionReason}}
      </p>

      {{#if rejectionMessage}}
        <p>
          <strong>Additional explanation:</strong><br />
          {{rejectionMessage}}
        </p>
      {{/if}}

      <p>
        Please review and revise accordingly if you plan to resubmit. You can
        reach out to us if you need more clarification.
      </p>

      <p>Best regards,<br />The Scopology Team</p>

      <div class="footer">
        &copy;
        {{year}}
        Scopology. All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>